# Changelog Fragments

Drop changelog fragments here. Towncrier will collect them on release.

## Fragment types

| Type          | Filename pattern    | Description              |
|---------------|---------------------|--------------------------|
| `feature`     | `123.feature.md`    | New features             |
| `bugfix`      | `123.bugfix.md`     | Bug fixes                |
| `improvement` | `123.improvement.md`| Enhancements             |
| `deprecation` | `123.deprecation.md`| Deprecated functionality |
| `breaking`    | `123.breaking.md`   | Breaking changes         |
| `security`    | `123.security.md`   | Security fixes           |
| `docs`        | `123.docs.md`       | Documentation updates    |
| `dev`         | `123.dev.md`        | Development changes      |
| `misc`        | `123.misc.md`       | Miscellaneous            |

## Usage

```bash
# Create a fragment
echo "Added widget support" > changes/42.feature.md

# Preview changelog
towncrier build --draft

# Build changelog (on release)
towncrier build --version 1.2.0
```
